==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*κρύπτω / kruptō / kroop'-to
A primary verb; to [[conceal]] (properly by covering): 

===Verb===
'''κρύπτω'''

#[[hide]] (self), keep secret, secret [-ly].

